Python 

def fibonacci(n):
    """"""
    if n <= 1:
        return n
    return fibonacci(n-1) + fibonacci(n-2)

# 
for i in range(10):
    print(f"F({i}) = {fibonacci(i)}")

JavaScript 

// 
async function fetchData(url) {
    try {
        const response = await fetch(url);
        const data = await response.json();
        return data;
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error:', error);
    }
}
